{"tid":686145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局勁Hea一句回覆:  不接受道具鈔申請","createTime":"2018-06-01T04:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T00:50:39.000Z","uid":49208,"like":124,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1dcffb14f61159dc7853875e1b42b53f0879a5","tid":686145,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"來源: from Monet Au<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10160524350235370&amp;set=a.378963185369.356480.528125369&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10160524350235370%26set%3Da.378963185369.356480.528125369%26type%3D3%26theater&d=FUGOQ%2FT1HVqIz2lEyQbz9ePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=4e8226b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10160524350235370&amp;set=a.378963185369.356480.528125369&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n睇FB見到, 新聞講到咩有晒手續申請, 原來早係2017年就有人申請過<br />\n但係金管局就一句Hea嵨人, 仲要根本就唔批你<br />\n<br />\n原文:<br />\n「上年全哥剛開始要打官司，提我話要申請叫我小心啲，我send email 去金管局問要點申請要申請幾耐得到以下截圖回覆，咁家陣打官司講撚到全世界都知有個好繁複既申請手續，又點撚解金管局會有人覆我係唔撚準印呢？ 我收到個email 之後又去問fso, fso又話可以申請，俾左個金管局好似叫楊生既電話我，咁樣來來往往我夠鐘拍喇，咪拍陰司紙囉end up」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/115815_95d2eecf0b37ebea12adc51873c0dd07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F115815_95d2eecf0b37ebea12adc51873c0dd07.jpg&h=0dea9d7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28e360b9f3d5442248568a3c8b5d8dfae309cc04","tid":686145,"uid":49208,"like":700,"dislike":1,"score":699,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/34066390_10155892865532961_1134101546326294528_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=1701c9f70b284aaf9d8767c73ab40a23&amp;oe=5B7E5080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt